med in western Oklahoma for over 100 years.  He lives in Cheyenne with his wife, Lynda.  They have three children and one grandchild.<ref>{{cite web|title=About Frank|url=http://www.lucas.house.gov/about-me/full-biography}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://lucas.house.gov/ Congressman Frank Lucas] official U.S. House site\n* [http://www.frankdlucas.com Frank Lucas for Congress]\n* {{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Oklahoma/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Frank_Lucas_%5BR-3%5D|Frank Lucas}}\n* {{C-SPAN|franklucas}}\n* {{CongLinks | congbio=l000491 | votesmart=27032 | fec=H4OK06056 | congress=frank-lucas/711 }}<!--\nLinks formerly displayed via the CongLinks template:\n* [http://ballotpedia.org/Frank_D._Lucas Biography] at [[Ballotpedia]]\n* [http://www.nndb.com/people/634/000039517 Biography] at [[NNDB]]\n* [http://www.govtrack.us/congress/members/400247 Congressional profile] at [[GovTrack]]\n* [http://www.opencongress.org/people/show/400247 Congressional profile] at [[Participatory Politics Foundation|OpenCongress]]\n* [http://www.rollcall.com/members/398.html Congressional profile] at ''[[Roll Call]]''\n* [http://www.opensecrets.org/politicians/summary.php?cid=N00005559 Financial information (federal office)] at [[Center for Responsive Politics|OpenSecrets.org]]\n* [http://apps.washingtonpost.com/politics/capitol-assets/member/frank-lucas Financial investments (personal)] at ''[[The Washington Post]]''\n* [http://www.legistorm.com/member/344/Rep_Frank_Lucas.html Staff salaries, trips and personal finance] at LegiStorm.com\n* [http://www.ontheissues.org/House/Frank_Dean_Lucas.htm Issue positions and quotes] at [[On the Issues]]\n* [http://www.c-spanvideo.org/person/35692 Appearances] on [[C-SPAN]] programs\n* [http://topics.bloomberg.com/frank-lucas Collected news and commentary] at ''[[Bloomberg News]]''\n* [http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/gIQAtwMLAP_topic.html Collected news and commentary] at '